frames.caption: A futuristic scene depicts a cybernetic orca leaping gracefully over a sleek, high-tech speedboat. The vibrant neon lights of both the orca and the boat illuminate the surrounding ocean and sky, creating a striking contrast against the natural elements.
frames.description: The image presents a futuristic and imaginative setting where technology and nature blend seamlessly. A cybernetic orca is captured mid-leap over a high-tech speedboat, both adorned with glowing neon lights. The scene is set against a backdrop of a cloudy sky and a dynamic ocean, suggesting a world where advanced technology coexists with natural beauty.

frames.caption: A majestic orca leaps out of the water next to a futuristic yacht, creating a dramatic splash under vibrant purple and pink lighting. The scene captures the dynamic motion of the orca against a backdrop of a cloudy sky, with the yacht's neon lights reflecting off the water.
frames.description: The scene is set in a futuristic marine environment where an orca is breaching near a high-tech yacht. The lighting is vivid, casting purple and pink hues across the water and sky, enhancing the dramatic and surreal atmosphere.
